casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Michelle Hamilton DAVY.
No. D-2747.
Supreme Court of the United States
Dec. 2, 2013.
Michelle Hamilton Davy, of Largo, Maryland, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring her to show cause why she should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
